### Plots API (with M:N Vegetable Relations)

### List all plots
GET http://localhost:8080/plots
Accept: application/json

### Get plot by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/plots/1
Accept: application/json

### Create plot (Garden ID = 1)
POST http://localhost:8080/plots
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "width": 10,
  "height": 5,
  "garden": { "id": 1 }
}

### Assign vegetables to plot (M:N)
PUT http://localhost:8080/plots/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "vegetables": [
    { "id": 1 },
    { "id": 2 }
  ]
}

### Fully update plot (incl Garden + Vegetables)
PUT http://localhost:8080/plots/2
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "width": 12,
  "height": 7,
  "garden": { "id": 1 },
  "vegetables": [
    { "id": 1 }
  ]
}

### Delete plot
DELETE http://localhost:8080/plots/1
